# Secret Management Rules
tags: ["secrets", "env", "security"]
appliesTo: ["GPT", "CursorAgent"]
enforce: true
priority: high

## Rules

- No secret values may be hardcoded in patches or scripts.
- All secrets must route through Vault or `.env` reference.
- All patches must use `${VAR_NAME}` for secrets, never plaintext.
- `.env.example` must be updated with each secret-dependent patch.